beer.beer_description:
Citra | Motueka | Krush

Our brewers, Erik and Mike, felt some of our recent DIPAs were a tad too sweet, so they've tweaked this one to strike that perfect balance. What you get is a DIPA bursting with sweet tropical fruit and citrus on your palate, without being sickly sweet. Plus, there's this cool, subtle vanilla note we reckon came from spunding the beer. Definitely something we need to look into more!
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
